					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-5">
            <h3 class="subtitle">SECURE GATEWAY</h3>
            <p>
				A central gateway acts as a firewall between external networks and in-vehicle networks. It also plays an important role in the implementation of secure over-the-air firmware updates.
			</p>
			<a href="/assets/documents/data/en/white-papers/Making-Full-Vehicle-OTA-Updates-Reality-WP.pdf" target="_blank" class="dtmGenLink" data-dtmName="SECURE GATEWAY - Read Whitepaper Button"><div class="btn">Read Whitepaper</div></a>
        </div>
    </div>
	
	<div class="row marg-bot-4x hideme">
        <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-push-5 col-lg-offset-1">
			<div class="overlay">
				<a href="/applications/solutions-for-the-iot-and-adas/automotive/secure-vehicle-architecture/in-vehicle-networks:IN-VEHICLE-NETWORKS" target="_blank" class="dtmGenLink" data-dtmName="SECURE NETWORKS - Image Link">
					<div class="img-heading">
						<img class="img-responsive" src="/assets/images/en/banners/Security-SecureNetwork.jpg" alt="SECURE NETWORKS" />
					</div>
				</a>
			</div>
        </div>      
        <div class="col-lg-5 col-lg-pull-5">
            <h3 class="subtitle">SECURE NETWORKS</h3>
            <p>
				Our secure networks layer uses bus monitoring and the cryptographic capabilities of an NXP transceiver or MCU to protect the communication over the in-vehicle networks.
			</p>
			<a href="/applications/solutions-for-the-iot-and-adas/automotive/secure-vehicle-architecture/in-vehicle-networks:IN-VEHICLE-NETWORKS" target="_blank" class="dtmGenLink" data-dtmName="SECURE NETWORKS - Learn More Button"><div class="btn">Learn More</div></a>
        </div>
    </div>
	
	<div class="row marg-bot-4x hideme">
